Third Department,

March. 1975

(March 3, 1975) In the Matter of George Jemzura, Petitioner, v. William Gordon, as Judge of the Chenango County Court, Respondent.

Petition dated December 30, 1974, dismissed sua sponte, without costs (see CPLR 7801, subds. 1, 2). Motion to dismiss petition denied as academic, without costs. Herlihy, P. J., Greenblott, Sweeney, Kane and Main, JJ., concur.
